resources.string: You need to tell us a bit about yoursefl.

You start with 20 min of running.

 then 10 min of cycling. 

 then a bit of stretching followed by max 10 push ups in 3 intervals.

 once you finished with it then 8 pull up on the machine.

 This will be your worm up once you done you should hed over to the weight lifting side n try bench press with just the bar.

 3 sets 5-6 reps a set

 after words try incline bench press if you can do the same amount of it as well.

 once you done with it if could not do it no problem, do dumbbell fly, same amount, afterwords do hammer with2kg weight dumbbell

 followed by bar pull.
